name: Blue Faith Planner Printable for traveler's notebook and Fauxdori, Faithdori, Bible journaling, Bible art journaling
description:
This is a digital file for a standard size fauxdori or travelers notebook.  The file will print on 8.5x11 paper and will need trimmed to size (2.75 bottom margin).  The file should be printed front and back, trimmed, and then stapled together in the center to form a booklet.

You are not purchasing a finished product.  You must download the file to print your own insert.

The planner printable includes a line at the top for the date and a place to write in what you are thanking God for today.  Along the left side of the page, there is a large box for prayers. On the right side, there is a To Do list bullet box and a box for memory keeping.  And across the bottom is an open box for Bible journaling inspiration.

If you would like this printable in a different color, please message me about a special order.

name: Long Day
description:
Weary and tired from a long day of training , wanting to be back in the stable settling in for the evening and perhaps catch up with his stable mates.

Acrylic paint on stretched canvas with a varnish finish, deep edge canvas painted.

W 31 cm L 35 cm depth 4.5 cm

This painting is ready to be hung up on your wall.

This horse is a wayward horse and you would really want to be wide awake and alert when near him, his a beautiful looking horse but just a little bit of a temper . This is my first attempt at getting him on canvas but I have roughed out a couple of ideas to paint in the coming weeks of him fully and it should be good.
